00:00:55.960 --> 00:00:57.070
What are you doing here?

00:00:59.030 --> 00:01:00.600
I heard from Ce

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:02.320
that you're inspecting here today.

00:01:03.030 --> 00:01:04.430
You haven't been back for a long time.

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:06.230
I booked a table
at an authentic restaurant

00:01:06.230 --> 00:01:07.310
on Beizheng Street

00:01:07.310 --> 00:01:07.840
in the old city

00:01:07.840 --> 00:01:09.000
to welcome you back.

00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:10.430
I also wish

00:01:11.710 --> 00:01:13.760
to strengthen the bond
between you brothers.

00:01:15.120 --> 00:01:17.310
You're truly his virtuous wife.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:19.350
But I wouldn't dare to attend

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.200
a personal dinner between you two.

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:24.840
Minghui,

00:01:24.840 --> 00:01:26.510
you'd better give up this thought.

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:33.950
Please do come at 8 PM tonight.

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:35.590
There's a special dish

00:01:36.480 --> 00:01:37.590
that you'll enjoy.

00:01:45.230 --> 00:01:46.200
Chu Minghui.

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.760
Why did you marry Gu Tongce?

00:02:10.030 --> 00:02:11.000
Gu Tongpei,

00:02:11.750 --> 00:02:13.190
I know what's on your mind.

00:02:14.030 --> 00:02:15.080
But I'm no longer someone

00:02:15.080 --> 00:02:16.560
worth you wasting your time.

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.560
I hope that when everything settles,

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.590
you can take Hongdou away from here.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:47.310
Mr. Gu,

00:02:47.310 --> 00:02:48.710
our men didn't find any abnormalities.

00:02:49.080 --> 00:02:51.000
Gu Tongce must have received word

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:52.000
and warned them beforehand.

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.150
As expected.

00:02:53.840 --> 00:02:55.560
If he gave himself away this easily,

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:56.710
he wouldn't be Gu Tongce.

00:02:56.870 --> 00:02:57.750
But I just overheard

00:02:57.750 --> 00:02:59.080
a few of his soldiers saying

00:02:59.080 --> 00:03:01.080
they're heading to Beizheng Street
for a show.

00:03:01.430 --> 00:03:02.470
What's that about?

00:03:05.910 --> 00:03:07.430
I booked a table
at an authentic restaurant

00:03:07.430 --> 00:03:08.800
on Beizheng Street

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:09.310
in the old city

00:03:09.310 --> 00:03:10.520
to welcome you back.

00:03:11.710 --> 00:03:13.310
Please do come tonight.

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.150
There's a special dish

00:03:15.710 --> 00:03:16.910
that you'll enjoy.

00:03:21.470 --> 00:03:24.470
Chu Minghui, was all this intentional?

00:03:27.630 --> 00:03:28.560
I'll be out for a while.

00:03:46.590 --> 00:03:47.430
Stop there!

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:49.400
- No...
- Get up!

00:03:49.680 --> 00:03:50.520
No!

00:03:50.710 --> 00:03:51.560
Hurry up.

00:03:52.150 --> 00:03:52.870
Take her back.

00:03:52.870 --> 00:03:54.080
Sir!

00:03:54.590 --> 00:03:55.430
Please let us go.

00:03:55.430 --> 00:03:56.800
Get lost!

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.630
Honey.

00:03:58.310 --> 00:04:00.240
- Stop the crying.
- Are you okay?

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:01.840
I'm taking your daughter

00:04:01.840 --> 00:04:03.000
to enjoy her life.

00:04:03.470 --> 00:04:05.190
Stop bawling.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:06.910
Get lost!

00:04:07.710 --> 00:04:09.190
Who are you?

00:04:09.470 --> 00:04:11.080
Don't you meddle in my business.

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.800
You're soldiers.

00:04:13.150 --> 00:04:14.560
How can you abduct innocent women?

00:04:16.190 --> 00:04:18.360
What are you talking about?

00:04:19.390 --> 00:04:20.630
We're recruiting girls

00:04:20.630 --> 00:04:22.310
to perform at the camp

00:04:22.310 --> 00:04:23.560
to boost morale.

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:25.720
What kind of performances?

00:04:25.800 --> 00:04:27.510
What else would it be?

00:04:28.510 --> 00:04:30.160
Strip shows, of course.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:35.720
I won't repeat myself.

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:37.360
Let them go.

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.920
We serve Commander Liu.

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.920
Stand in our way,

00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:49.920
and you're defying
the whole Jiang City army.

00:05:03.160 --> 00:05:04.510
Who are you on earth?

00:05:04.830 --> 00:05:06.920
We're the Inspector's
direct troops.

00:05:07.240 --> 00:05:08.070
This is

00:05:08.560 --> 00:05:10.560
our Military Commissioner
who just arrived.

00:05:11.190 --> 00:05:13.480
Commander Liu ordered to force women
into prostitution.

00:05:13.750 --> 00:05:14.750
Arrest him immediately.

00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:15.560
Yes, sir!

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:17.360
Gu Tongpei!

00:05:18.070 --> 00:05:19.750
You're a mere Commissioner.

00:05:20.270 --> 00:05:22.800
By seniority,
you should show some respect.

00:05:23.750 --> 00:05:25.510
I have connections
and influence aplenty.

00:05:26.120 --> 00:05:28.310
Release me now if you know your place.

00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:30.870
Or you will be very sorry.

00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:40.200
You've sat idle in your post for years.

00:05:40.270 --> 00:05:41.600
Someone should've taught you a lesson.

00:05:42.310 --> 00:05:43.240
Commander Liu.

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:48.070
You are truly oblivious

00:05:48.870 --> 00:05:50.600
to your own men

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:51.630
being such scoundrels.

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:54.920
I'm sorry.

00:05:55.310 --> 00:05:57.310
It was my failure of oversight.

00:06:00.560 --> 00:06:01.310
Tongpei,

00:06:01.870 --> 00:06:03.630
regarding Commander Liu,

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:05.560
I've suspended him.

00:06:08.070 --> 00:06:08.920
Why?

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:11.560
Are you covering for him?

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:15.190
It's not like that.

00:06:16.190 --> 00:06:18.310
I'm preserving Father's reputation.

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.190
After all, Commander Liu

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:22.310
was Father's trusted aide.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.270
Come home for dinner tonight.

00:06:27.870 --> 00:06:29.560
Many things
are just misunderstandings.

00:06:30.190 --> 00:06:31.360
As long as it's all cleared up.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:52.560
I'm leaving, Tongpei.

00:07:00.310 --> 00:07:01.750
We finally managed to catch him.

00:07:01.870 --> 00:07:03.160
Are we really letting him go so easily?

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:05.270
This whole thing

00:07:05.600 --> 00:07:07.950
was done based on information
from Chu Minghui.

00:07:08.310 --> 00:07:10.070
I'm not sure what she's after.

00:07:10.870 --> 00:07:12.270
We can only release Commander Liu

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.560
to test her reaction.

00:07:14.430 --> 00:07:16.920
Let's find out
whether she's foe or friend.

00:07:17.070 --> 00:07:17.720
Butâ€¦

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.800
After all these years,

00:07:19.240 --> 00:07:20.190
we've changed.

00:07:21.190 --> 00:07:22.510
Maybe she's changed too.

00:07:39.270 --> 00:07:41.480
Welcome home, Tongpei.

00:07:41.920 --> 00:07:42.950
Didn't expect this, did you?

00:07:43.310 --> 00:07:45.920
You met Minghui just two days ago,

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:48.120
and here you are meeting again so soon.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.160
Two days ago,

00:07:55.160 --> 00:07:55.870
I happened

00:07:56.190 --> 00:07:58.160
to run into Minghui
and Hongdou on the street.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:00.070
We exchanged a brief greeting.

00:08:01.830 --> 00:08:03.480
You're so lucky to have them.

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:10.800
Let's not just stand here.

00:08:11.040 --> 00:08:12.560
Tongce specially asked me

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:14.920
to properly prepare this first banquet

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:16.600
since your return.

00:08:17.310 --> 00:08:18.560
Let's go.

00:08:19.870 --> 00:08:20.920
First?

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:23.750
After you.

00:08:48.320 --> 00:08:49.030
Tongpei,

00:08:49.870 --> 00:08:51.200
there were some misunderstandings

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.510
about what happened last time.

00:08:53.550 --> 00:08:54.550
Let's finish this cup of wine

00:08:54.750 --> 00:08:56.670
and forget all that.

00:08:58.390 --> 00:08:59.270
I'm on official duty.

00:08:59.670 --> 00:09:00.790
I'll drink tea instead of wine.

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:07.870
Tongpei,

00:09:08.630 --> 00:09:09.720
try this.

00:09:10.000 --> 00:09:12.200
It's Minghui's specialty.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:22.750
Seems I was right to come here.

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.960
It truly is an excellent dish.

00:09:25.720 --> 00:09:26.910
Whether the dish is good

00:09:27.240 --> 00:09:28.390
depends on

00:09:28.390 --> 00:09:30.120
whether it suits your taste.

00:09:41.750 --> 00:09:42.550
Minghui,

00:09:43.480 --> 00:09:46.320
when you met with Tongpei last time,

00:09:46.600 --> 00:09:47.750
what did you talk about?

00:09:51.120 --> 00:09:52.910
Minghui was actually
looking for a chance

00:09:53.270 --> 00:09:55.150
to mend the relationship
between us as brothers.

00:09:55.720 --> 00:09:57.360
All for your sake.

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:02.750
Is that so? How thoughtful.

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.550
Thank you for caring about me.

00:10:10.910 --> 00:10:11.960
It just occurred to me

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:13.390
I still have matters to handle.

00:10:13.670 --> 00:10:14.670
I shall take my leave.

00:10:15.030 --> 00:10:16.000
Just a moment.

00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:18.750
Ce had me prepare a gift for you.

00:10:20.030 --> 00:10:22.480
How about I take Tongpei
to the study to fetch it?

00:10:26.670 --> 00:10:27.480
Go ahead.

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:48.960
Thank you.

00:10:49.870 --> 00:10:51.600
How thoughtful of you.

00:10:52.150 --> 00:10:53.550
You chose the restaurant yesterday

00:10:53.790 --> 00:10:55.000
with great care too.

00:10:57.320 --> 00:10:58.720
You don't come back often.

00:10:59.080 --> 00:11:01.790
Of course I had to choose carefully.

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.840
So you knew

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:05.670
there was quite a show to see there?

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.750
How do you watch a show at a restaurant?

00:11:09.480 --> 00:11:11.720
I don't understand what you mean.

00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:17.750
I've found out the truth

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:20.000
about what happened four years ago.

00:11:20.630 --> 00:11:21.440
Chu Minghui,

00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:25.000
I'm sorry for what I did to you.

00:11:26.390 --> 00:11:27.910
Can you please not hold it against me?

00:11:38.870 --> 00:11:40.000
It's been years.

00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:43.120
Let's drop the habit
of speaking in circles.

00:12:04.080 --> 00:12:07.480
Uncle, you're visiting us again.

00:12:09.480 --> 00:12:10.790
Smart girl.

00:12:10.870 --> 00:12:11.960
You only met me once,

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:12.720
and you remember me.

00:12:13.270 --> 00:12:13.910
Twice.

00:12:14.750 --> 00:12:16.630
I found a photo of you

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:20.550
in Mother's box.

00:12:26.480 --> 00:12:29.120
It's a photo of you and Ce
that he asked me to pack away.

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:31.630
I have matters to do

00:12:32.320 --> 00:12:33.600
and won't see you out.

00:12:38.000 --> 00:12:41.320
Chu Minghui, what is truly on your mind?

00:12:47.080 --> 00:12:47.870
Madam.

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:50.510
Take Miss Hongdou upstairs

00:12:50.510 --> 00:12:51.480
and tuck her in.

00:12:51.630 --> 00:12:51.960
Okay.

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:53.960
The Military Governor and the Commander
still have much to discuss tonight.

00:12:54.240 --> 00:12:55.480
After serve the last dish,

00:12:55.910 --> 00:12:57.080
you may all retire and rest.

00:12:57.080 --> 00:12:57.750
Understood.

00:12:58.200 --> 00:13:00.600
Hongdou, be good
and go to bed first, okay?

00:13:02.670 --> 00:13:03.480
Wait.

00:13:05.750 --> 00:13:06.960
Tell the kitchen

00:13:07.240 --> 00:13:08.320
the last dish, the roasted leg of lamb,

00:13:08.320 --> 00:13:09.200
doesn't need carving.

00:13:09.480 --> 00:13:11.270
Just set the knives and forks properly.

00:13:11.390 --> 00:13:12.870
I'll serve it personally.

00:13:12.870 --> 00:13:13.910
Yes.

00:13:43.790 --> 00:13:44.440
Mr. Liu,

00:13:45.630 --> 00:13:46.120
please.

00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:53.120
Who does Gu Tongpei think he is?

00:13:53.270 --> 00:13:54.440
He just took the order of someone big

00:13:54.440 --> 00:13:55.910
and dared to meddle in my business?

00:13:56.200 --> 00:13:58.750
The Inspector wants to bring me down.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.550
That's why they sent Gu Tongpei.

00:14:00.870 --> 00:14:03.600
You should be cautious from now on.

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:06.670
It's just having a few women for fun.

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:08.390
What's the big deal?

00:14:08.840 --> 00:14:10.270
Which of the higher-ups
hasn't done this?

00:14:10.670 --> 00:14:11.480
Exactly.

00:14:11.840 --> 00:14:15.120
It is only human nature.

00:14:15.510 --> 00:14:17.910
No one else has the right
to point fingers at it.

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:19.600
It's just

00:14:19.630 --> 00:14:21.120
Ce regards you as one of his own.

00:14:21.550 --> 00:14:23.150
He simply hopes
you'll keep some restraint.

00:14:24.630 --> 00:14:26.550
What restraint can there be

00:14:26.790 --> 00:14:28.510
between men and women?

00:14:28.550 --> 00:14:29.750
Who can really control it?

00:14:30.150 --> 00:14:30.960
Mr. Gu,

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:32.600
can you?

00:14:32.870 --> 00:14:33.670
Mr. Liu,

00:14:34.390 --> 00:14:36.360
it's really been hard for you.

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:37.750
After all,

00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:39.550
you and your soldiers
are swamped with military duties.

00:14:39.750 --> 00:14:41.670
It's perfectly reasonable
to relax occasionally.

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:46.550
Exactly.

00:14:47.030 --> 00:14:48.840
Even you, a woman, understand this.

00:14:48.840 --> 00:14:50.510
What's Gu Tongpei
even putting on airs for?

00:14:51.000 --> 00:14:51.790
Besides,

00:14:52.390 --> 00:14:54.270
those women aren't at a loss.

00:14:54.480 --> 00:14:55.600
What I've raised

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:57.550
is a troop of vigorous, virile soldiers.

00:14:58.200 --> 00:15:00.120
Mr. Liu, don't let it get to you.

00:15:01.440 --> 00:15:02.750
You've been treated unfairly.

00:15:06.910 --> 00:15:07.750
Mr. Gu,

00:15:09.080 --> 00:15:11.360
with such a fine wife tending to you,

00:15:12.390 --> 00:15:15.550
we all envy you.

00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:19.080
I've raised a force
of strong, able-bodied men,

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:21.150
not a bunch of eunuchs.

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:23.720
If it's in place,

00:15:23.790 --> 00:15:25.600
it's bound to see action.

00:15:27.120 --> 00:15:30.120
Only eunuchs would behave themselves.

